2. Build & Install Phase

Point to Build / Install.

“This process starts when developers check in their code into GitLab.
Once the code is committed, Jenkins automatically triggers the CI/CD pipeline.”

“At this stage the system performs the build and install process, packaging the application and deploying it into the target environment.”

“If the build fails, the pipeline stops and a defect is raised immediately.”

